Package: socialinfrascorer
Type: Package
Title: Minimal Supabase Client for Social Infrastructure Scorecard
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Timothy", "Fraser", email = "timothy@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Small client package for read-only access to selected SCORECARD
    Supabase/PostgreSQL data through Supabase Auth and Data API endpoints.
    Supports authenticated user signup/signin, polygon lookup by osm_id or
    location_id/area_id/place_name, place-name location lookup, and bounded
    scorecard_result downloads.
